{"tid":2075251,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"歐盟：黨安法不符基本法和中共對國際的承諾；習：中歐是朋友","createTime":"2020-06-22T17:02:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T01:00:46.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"13bdcf88c3622cc6fed6ae14fc213f76d28db43e","tid":2075251,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T17:02:43.000Z","msg":"歐盟：港區國安法不符基本法和中國對國際的承諾<br />\n23.06.2020 00:42<br />\n<br />\n中歐領導人以視像方式舉行會面，國家主席習近平、總理李克強，與歐洲理事會主席米歇爾、歐盟委員會主席馮德萊恩開會。米歇爾在會面後表示，歐盟對中國在香港實施國安法表示極大關注，擔心會影響到本港的自治以及國際金融中心地位。歐盟表示，會上提到多項人權議題，包括嚴重關切北京推動港區國安法，認為不符合基本法和中國對國際的承諾，促請北京確保香港的政治多元、民主和人權水平。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟又提到中國拘留銅鑼灣書店的瑞典籍前股東桂民海，以及兩名加拿大公民康明凱和邁克爾斯帕弗。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1317190&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1317190%26csid%3D261_341&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7gNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=a91042dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1317190&amp;csid=261_341</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n習近平：中歐沒有根本利害衝突 合作遠大於競爭<br />\n23.06.2020 00:54<br />\n<br />\n國家主席習近平，與歐洲理事會主席米歇爾和歐盟委員會主席馮德萊恩舉行視像對話。習近平指，自從疫情發生以來，中國和歐盟相互支持、相互幫助，中方願同歐方攜手努力，推動「後疫情時代」中歐關係更加穩健成熟，邁向更高水平。習近平強調，中歐沒有根本利害衝突，合作遠大於競爭，共識遠大於分歧，雙方要相互尊重、求同存異、和而不同，不斷增進彼此理解和信任，在合作中擴大共同利益，在發展中破解難題，打造更具世界影響力的中歐全面戰略伙伴關係。<br />\n<br />\n米歇爾和馮德萊恩就表示，歐方願意本著坦誠的態度，同中方開展戰略對話，擴大共識。歐方願同中方就疫苗研發、復工復產加強合作，擴大雙邊貿易規模，盡快達成歐中投資協定，為盡早克服疫情影響、促進世界經濟復蘇作出努力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1317210&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1317210%26csid%3D261_341&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7gNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=0b366e01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1317210&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"5bd8aa4dc9342d284ef7c7f61dfe1921104086bd","tid":2075251,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T17:03:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />."},{"pid":"3fe8c97db2be530b875670d72c288c10971ff970","tid":2075251,"uid":34065,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T17:05:50.000Z","msg":"笑撚死 真正牛頭唔搭馬嘴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08d8d38e3b49df18838dd142ac1ca381a938e829","tid":2075251,"uid":287745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T17:06:01.000Z","msg":"習總係到講乜野<br />\n九唔搭八"},{"pid":"55a9b046d8aaaf8ab700a583b8428c7edb2d9d35","tid":2075251,"uid":284699,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T17:06:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ERXuEpmUYAA4WmQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FERXuEpmUYAA4WmQ.jpg&h=1630105d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"933ca8ac7257b81ffe323f0ccbb3e68efa10af40","tid":2075251,"uid":44071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T17:08:21.000Z","msg":"咁仲洗乜開會？<br />\n各自講一段 send 俾對方 is ok"},{"pid":"178d48d015a512c9ab4089d039b1dd3e504e50d3","tid":2075251,"uid":131188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T17:09:26.000Z","msg":"點解唔係石頭腳嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8088b1feebda0c0fab08a9cf544a6d8a71a6cb60","tid":2075251,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T00:23:42.000Z","msg":"俾錢咪朋友"},{"pid":"355a2f6d3f33e0fa970290bbf27b32c9b8b94546","tid":2075251,"uid":68620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T00:26:42.000Z","msg":"維尼：講，要幾多錢，比個數我<br />\n歐盟：我錢又要，香港又要，完"},{"pid":"93d471a324d8bafabf556d948d1b8533803d6401","tid":2075251,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T00:34:38.000Z","msg":"毒撚：朋友<img src=\"/assets/face